name: OBPP Standards Audit
description: Order-Based Pick & Pack. 25 orders, 40 lines, 55 units. 1 Job = 1 Order.
explanation: Per-order Job OH + Location + SKU multipliers. Packing OH + Order + Unit per order.

name: PUTW Standards Audit
description: Put-Wall 3-Phase. 25 orders, 40 lines, 55 units. 1 Batch Pick -> 1 Sort -> 25 Pack.
explanation: Batch Pick OH + Loc + SKU. Sort OH + per-unit. Pack OH + Order + Unit per order.

name: MICP Standards Audit
description: Multi-Item Carton Profiling. 25 orders in 3 carts (max 12/cart). 40 lines, 55 units.
explanation: Per-cart Pick OH + Loc + SKU + Line. Pack OH + Order + Unit per order.

name: SICP Standards Audit
description: Single-Item Carton Profiling. 10 single-item orders, 1 cart, 1 loc, 1 SKU.
explanation: 1 Cart Pick OH + Loc + SKU + Line. Pack OH + Order + Unit per order.

name: SIBP Standards Audit
description: Single-Item Batch Pick. 10 single-item orders, 1 batch job, 1 loc, 1 SKU.
explanation: 1 Batch Pick OH + Loc + SKU. Pack OH + Order + Unit per order.

name: IIBP Standards Audit
description: Item-In-Box Profiling. 10 single-item orders, 1 SKU group(s).
explanation: 1 Pick + 1 Pack job per unique SKU. OH + Loc + SKU per pick job. OH + Orders*Order + Units*Unit per pack job.

name: IOBP Standards Audit
description: Identical Order Batch. 25 orders grouped into 10 identical SKU+Unit combos.
explanation: 1 Pick job per combo. OH + Loc + SKU per pick job. Pack OH + Order + Unit per order.
